import { ChangeDetectionStrategy, Component, Input } from '@angular/core';

  selector: 'story-basic-button',
  template: `
    <button
      aui-button
      [plain]="plain"
      [round]="round"
      [disabled]="disabled"
      [loading]="loading"
      [size]="size"
    >
      默认按钮

    <button
      aui-button="primary"
      [plain]="plain"
      [round]="round"
      [disabled]="disabled"
      [loading]="loading"
      [size]="size"
    >
      主要按钮
    </button>
    <button
      aui-button="success"
      [plain]="plain"
      [round]="round"
      [disabled]="disabled"
      [loading]="loading"
      [size]="size"
    >

      aui-button="danger"
      [plain]="plain"
      [round]="round"
      [disabled]="disabled"
      [loading]="loading"
      [size]="size"

})

  /**

  /**
